thonline\/2013\/08\/29\/cursing-by-name-laan\/","url_meta":{"origin":32178,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Curses: Prohibition of cursing people by name","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, raised his head from the last bowing in dawn prayer, saying, \u201cO Allah, curse this person, and this person, and this person,\u201d Then, Allah revealed the verse, \u201cYou have no say in the matter. It is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2973,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/20\/islam-pillar-prayer-summit-jihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":32178,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Its pillar is prayer, its peak is jihad","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: I was traveling with the Prophet one morning, close to him as we journeyed together, and I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, tell me of a deed that will admit me into Paradise and keep me away from the Hellfire.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37570,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/19\/salah-3-times\/","url_meta":{"origin":32178,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet stresses the greatness of prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: A man came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he asked him about the best of deeds. The Prophet said, \u201cPrayer.\u201d The man said, \u201cThen what?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThen prayer.\u201d The man said, \u201cThen what?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThen\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13527,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/11\/virtue-fajr-jamaah-jumuah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32178,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fajr: Dawn prayer in congregation on Friday","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 11, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the best of prayers to Allah is the dawn prayer in congregation on Friday.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 2790 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5660,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/29\/supplication-in-witr-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":32178,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Witr: The Prophet\u2019s supplication in Witr prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ubayy ibn Ka\u2019b reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, when he finished his Witr prayer with invocations of peace, he would say, \u201cGlory to the King, the Holy.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1430 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0643\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14050,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/07\/fajr-salat-better-nawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":32178,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Fajr: Prayer better than sleep, prayer better than sleep","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 7, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Mahdhurah reported: I was the caller to prayer for the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him. I would say during the first call of the dawn prayer, \u201cCome to success. Prayer is better than sleep. Prayer is better than sleep. Allah is the greatest. Allah is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32178","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=32178"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32178\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=32178"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=32178"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=32178"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}